---
// Final CTA — closer with re-anchored value prop
---
<section class="final-cta">
  <div class="container final-grid">

    <div class="final-text reveal">
      <p class="eyebrow">Two paths from here</p>
      <h2 class="h-closer">
        See If We're<br/>
        a <em>Fit.</em>
      </h2>
      <p class="lede">
        Fifteen minutes on the calendar tells us — and you — whether the system fits your shop. If it does, the install starts in days, not months. If it doesn't, you'll leave the call with the audit, no charge, no follow-up sequence.
      </p>

      <div class="final-ctas">
        <a href="/book" class="cta" data-cta-source="final-primary">
          See If We're a Fit
          <span class="cta-arrow" aria-hidden="true">→</span>
        </a>
        <a href="/how-it-works" class="cta-ghost" data-cta-source="final-secondary">See the System</a>
      </div>
    </div>

    <aside class="final-aside reveal" aria-label="Build-Right Guarantee">
      <p class="kpi-label mono">The Build-Right Guarantee</p>
      <p class="guarantee-h">
        If we miss the install milestones, we keep building until we hit them. <em>On us.</em>
      </p>
      <ul class="guarantee-list">
        <li><span class="dot live"></span><span>System operational inside 30 days</span></li>
        <li><span class="dot live"></span><span>First leads inside the first 30 days, or we keep working</span></li>
        <li><span class="dot live"></span><span>Month-to-month, no long-term lock-in</span></li>
      </ul>
    </aside>

  </div>
</section>

<style>
.final-cta { padding-block: var(--section-y); position: relative; overflow: hidden; }
.final-cta::before {
  content: '';
  position: absolute;
  inset: 0;
  background: radial-gradient(ellipse 80% 60% at 70% 50%, rgba(212, 169, 85, 0.06), transparent 65%);
  pointer-events: none;
}
.final-grid {
  display: grid;
  grid-template-columns: minmax(0, 1.4fr) minmax(0, 1fr);
  gap: clamp(48px, 6vw, 96px);
  align-items: center;
  position: relative;
  z-index: 1;
}
.final-text { display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 24px; }
.final-ctas { display: flex; gap: 16px; flex-wrap: wrap; margin-top: 16px; }

.final-aside {
  background: var(--bg-elev);
  border: 1px solid var(--gold);
  padding: 36px 32px;
  display: flex;
  flex-direction: column;
  gap: 20px;
}
.guarantee-h {
  font-family: var(--serif);
  font-size: clamp(24px, 2.4vw, 32px);
  font-weight: 400;
  line-height: 1.25;
  color: var(--ink);
}
.guarantee-list { list-style: none; display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 14px; padding-top: 16px; border-top: 1px solid var(--rule); }
.guarantee-list li { display: flex; align-items: flex-start; gap: 10px; font-size: 15px; font-weight: 300; color: var(--ink-dim); line-height: 1.5; }
.guarantee-list .dot { margin-top: 8px; }

@media (max-width: 880px) {
  .final-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
}
</style>
